{"tid":2369850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【公務員宣誓】港台員工：條文與新聞工作有衝突 如「緊箍咒」隨時被清算","createTime":"2021-01-17T13:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T13:24:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12e48d933cc8f0f6a4fb3d4ab0f9d58fc0f2ef5c","tid":2369850,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:24:20.000Z","msg":"屬商經局轄下的香港電台，大部分新聞編採人員同屬公務員職系，多名港台員工憂慮，聲明中限制言論的條文與新聞工作有衝突，「新聞人員的專業是報道真相，好多時是政府不想你報道的&hellip;我們可以多大程度上報到這些新聞，但又不違反政府立場？」亦有員工指，條文範圍十分模糊，有如「緊箍咒」限制日常採訪，「可能我問一條問題，內容不是我個人看法，但只要有人懷疑就可以去篤灰。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5-%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87%E8%88%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%A6%82-%E7%B7%8A%E7%AE%8D%E5%92%92-%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%25A6%2582-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E7%25AE%258D%25E5%2592%2592-%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25AE%2597%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=14798895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%25A6%2582-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E7%25AE%258D%25E5%2592%2592-%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25AE%2597%2F&h=55c72a05\" target